{"tid":1834792,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我哋好似唔記得咗一啲零風險而好有效嘅文宣方法？","createTime":"2020-01-22T14:34:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T14:59:00.000Z","uid":307203,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1a414711b38dbdb3655d2d75988b0bd1945be28b","tid":1834792,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:34:31.000Z","msg":"1.打著紅旗反紅旗<br />\n<br />\n雖然連儂牆近排不斷被破壞，而好多文宣都被破壞，但係唯有一種文宣好似一直都存在，就係打著紅旗反紅旗文宣<br />\n<br />\n好似以下呢啲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/22/221459_5cb52e58c3251ff06712d7d7a0c482dd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F22%2F221459_5cb52e58c3251ff06712d7d7a0c482dd.jpg&h=29d7f2b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UNY6mGk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUNY6mGk.jpg&h=c31b3012&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/22/221544_6d79b0e33b322aca8096007c39f59a30.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F22%2F221544_6d79b0e33b322aca8096007c39f59a30.jpg&h=17300582&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bzmPjth.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbzmPjth.jpg&h=1e61e852&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nnnEtk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nnnEtk.jpg&h=1542a817&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hcjAZtn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhcjAZtn.jpg&h=4ab8e7c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fDi93U7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfDi93U7.jpg&h=8e40cf1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/22/221649_9a56448020ef926d1a7e75d084d918b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F22%2F221649_9a56448020ef926d1a7e75d084d918b8.jpg&h=518f123b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/504UvAh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F504UvAh.jpg&h=52c456a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QXEEGGZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQXEEGGZ.jpg&h=b19f927b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4hGchfN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4hGchfN.jpg&h=efa7b477&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YkWS1Hx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYkWS1Hx.jpg&h=01a82f62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vrW38nz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvrW38nz.jpg&h=b6c50ed8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/feUQOnB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfeUQOnB.jpg&h=bf3df579&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6rpYcPh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6rpYcPh.jpg&h=b037554b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zZHOz2F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzZHOz2F.jpg&h=23b29619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JjQwxPw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJjQwxPw.jpg&h=b302684a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/22/221957_25abb75e892ae43ede715ca03c43e2fa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F22%2F221957_25abb75e892ae43ede715ca03c43e2fa.jpg&h=f060a7f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZEUxhgn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZEUxhgn.jpg&h=df4a03ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DMGDcP3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDMGDcP3.png&h=eb3dab70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/01/22/222308_500e0f959398af34f738021631627d24.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F01%2F22%2F222308_500e0f959398af34f738021631627d24.png&h=666c5499&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋文宣除咗要穩定軍心之外，都要增加支持自己一方嘅聲音，而藍絲主要分為利益藍同真心藍，而對付真心藍嘅最有效文宣就係呢種啦<br />\n<br />\n貼喺連儂牆又少人夠膽破壞，放喺藍絲Facebook page或者 group 搞分化亦得"},{"pid":"01a156ab10a6ec98862a436d00cd04f827fac56e","tid":1834792,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:43:50.000Z","msg":"2.Phone in 節目<br />\n<br />\n呢個亦都係零風險同埋有效嘅方法，下面比較長，希望大家可以耐心睇落去<br />\n<br />\n1.點解要用Phone in 節目去文宣呢?<br />\nA.制衡返紅媒洗腦<br />\n<br />\n大部分聽收音機嘅都係上咗年紀嘅人(當中𣎴乏藍黃)，既然未必阻到佢哋夜晚睇cctvb,方向報吸收維穩資訊，佢哋上下晝係會開收音機做BGM，所以電台起到一定文宣作用，一定要用電台講返事實出嚟，如警甴點打人同擾民<br />\n<br />\n解釋返勇武行動，如自衛嘅原因,點解要針對黨鐵同親中商戶,務求一定要好似71衝擊立法會咁,了解前因後果<br />\n<br />\nB.文宣效果擴大<br />\n好多揸車既人、屋企主婦、老人家、茶餐廳、的士、小巴佬都係聽收音機，同埋好多商戶無電視都會開收音機<br />\n另外可能有啲節目會將你嘅意見放落去佢哋嘅宣傳聲帶,可以喺唔同時間播放<br />\n<br />\n2.如何提高駁入直播室嘅成功率?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1587823/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1587823/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n3.發言方式<br />\n發言嘅方式都有好多種嘅，不過我哋要針對性咁做，以下有三大方式<br />\n<br />\nA.直腸直肚(For 黃)<br />\n只係講返我哋嘅意見，用嚟穩定軍心<br />\n<br />\nB.扮各打五十大板(For 中立,淺藍)<br />\n角色扮演:老師，家長，銀髮族，專業人士<br />\n節奏語調:唔好太有個人感情，要不偏不倚<br />\n首先扮中立，最後總結都是偏袒支持個邊，係個政府唔聽民意，官逼民反<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nC.陶傑曲線抽水大法(For 淺藍，深藍)<br />\n<br />\n講話要有藝術，要反諷，用官方腔調，誇張化。<br />\n<br />\n1.真心藍<br />\n例如要好似劉夢熊咁樣，話嗰啲為國家添煩添亂，鍾意嘅話可以用返偉大領袖毛主席或者鄧小平嘅名言<br />\n<br />\n2.利益藍<br />\n只要啲極左路線嘅說話，令到佢哋發現切身利益受損<br />\n<br />\n睇咗咁多係咪好想立即去表達自己嘅意見呢?<br />\n<br />\n如果大家驚講錯嘢，可以試下去d100 phone in 練習<br />\n<br />\nD100:<br />\n0800-1100 D100 PBS台&amp;香港台<br />\n風波裏的茶杯 Phone in 電話 :1831 138<br />\n<br />\n1700-2000 D100 PBS台<br />\n左右大局 Phone in 電話 :1831 138<br />\n<br />\n實戰就打下面<br />\n<br />\n港台:<br />\n0800-1000 香港電台第一台<br />\n千禧年代 / Phone in 電話: 1872311<br />\n<br />\n1700-2000 香港電台第一台<br />\n自由風自由Phone / Phone in 電話: 1872311<br />\n<br />\n商台:<br />\n0630-0700, 0715-1000 雷霆881 (陳志雲版)<br />\n0800-1000 叱咤903 (潘小濤版)<br />\n在晴朗的一天出發 / Phone in 電話: 1872881 (陳) / 1872903 (潘)<br />\n<br />\nNow:<br />\n09:30-12:00 時事全方位 Now新聞台 1833298"},{"pid":"e9c550bc8c93cb8f82fe964992c3dca965410ce0","tid":1834792,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:44:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c001caf6409cd4f040286a3d66abb7b85b42fae5","tid":1834792,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"858f9788da6035e602b93d64fc730f1e86983616","tid":1834792,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:44:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac55b61868e9e234ad31fcd30c23b5b605883ca2","tid":1834792,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:52:21.000Z","msg":"而且打著紅旗反紅旗嘅未開發完，仲有大量 題材可以發掘，因為中共領導人全部喺建國前，都講過大量民主自由嘅空話同支持西方自由世界嘅讚美說話，只係為咗氹班自由派支持中共<br />\n<br />\n唔信睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/00u7U1r2wHQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F00u7U1r2wHQ&d=UWp4lduD54HchuVgBglmzb9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=d2fec20e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/00u7U1r2wHQ</a>"},{"pid":"0035b8540742af8081c7117ecddf08882ae2f13e","tid":1834792,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:57:52.000Z","msg":"3. 社交媒體<br />\n<br />\n【簡易文宣】本土戰線&mdash;FaceBook!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1648722\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1648722</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nTwitterhelpbot 及Twitter 遊戲攻略 (不定期更新)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1673862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1673862</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bda2b3f36628d665fa3097d04f3a49c253e56ef2","tid":1834792,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T14:59:00.000Z","msg":"希望大家可以睇到幫手推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\np 牌推唔啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}